<h2 id="live-it-out">Live It Out</h2>
<p class="lead">End each week with a challenge to take action. Lead your group to help each person identify their next steps.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Going forward, how will you make kneeling a more regular posture of worship?</li>
  <li>What changes in your own worship habits have you already seen as a result of this series? What changes do you plan to continue to make?</li>
  <li>How will you make worship a priority in your life? How will the four postures from this series be a part of that?</li>
</ul>
